<h2>The Challenge: A Restaurant Lost in the Digital Noise</h2>
<strong>Meet Bella's Bistro</strong> (name changed for privacy), a family-owned Italian restaurant in Parramatta that had been serving authentic cuisine for over 15 years. Despite having loyal local customers and excellent food, the restaurant was struggling with:

<p>- <strong>Declining foot traffic</strong> due to increased competition and changing consumer habits
