<li><strong>Loss of revenue</strong> during COVID-19 lockdowns with no viable takeaway ordering system</p></li>
</ul>
<p>The owners, Maria and Giuseppe, realized they needed to embrace digital transformation or risk losing their business. They approached Cosmos Web Tech with a clear goal: increase online orders and improve their digital presence to compete with larger chain restaurants and delivery platforms.</p>

